{
  "stem": "11000.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And if the SS person in charge thought that you didn't look right or you weren't physically able or capable, then there was a truck standing there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you had to go up on the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When the truck was full, then the truck went back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the truck came back with the same amount of people, let's say, who were new arrivals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this was a constant exchange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That situation was always very sad, because you knew and they knew once you get on that truck what the end was gonna be.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And you never would see them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And some of the ones that had to get up on the truck, you knew for so long and went through for such long periods.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And you always felt bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And those were very sad moments, I would say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we don't know for sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the general [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] idea was they went straight to the gas chamber, because I don't know anybody that I knew who went on that truck.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know any of those that survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never saw any of them ever again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Work was very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We [? do ?] [? had ?] to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was hard physical work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, food never was enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After we went back to work, we could volunteer to do additional kitchen work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were allowed to peel potatoes or peel vegetables for the guards for their food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, you tried to volunteer because that gave you an opportunity that you were able to steal a few things and eat it while you were doing it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When you left the kitchen, you were checked to make sure that you didn't take any food with you.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
